<C>__{burns}
<D>__{you drooling idiot! what do you mean, you're getting out! there are three hundred and sixty five days in the year one can get married but how many times have you got a murderer locked up in a desk? once in a lifetime! hildy, you've got the whole city by the seat of the pants!}
<C>__{hildy}
<D>__{i know, but }
<C>__{burns}
<P>__{(interrupting)}
