<D>__{don't get technical at a time like this! do you realize what you've done? you've taken a city that's been graft ridden for forty years under the same old gang and with this yarn you're kicking 'em out and giving us a chance to have the same kind of government that new york's having under la guardia! we'll make such monkeys out of these ward heelers next tuesday that nobody'll vote for them not even their wives!}
<C>__{hildy}
<P>__{(the fire upon her)}
